ComicInfo.Title: Fractured Part three
ComicInfo.Summary: Cable sends Deadpool off to get his backup data archives in his hotel. when Deadpool gets there he has a faceoff with Senyaka. Meanwhile, Cable has to fight off Gambit and Sunfire which in the end he fails, sort of. When Deadpool finally gets the backup, which is a little blue statue, he bodyslides to somewhere safe where he can use the backup. From what we know Cable has been done in by the Cajon and Sunfire.
